1575605 - Crash in [@ java.lang.NullPointerException: at org.mozilla.gecko.home.TabMenuStripLayout.onPageSelected(TabMenuStripLayout.java)] r=VladBaicu\n\nNow performing a sanity check after grabbing the child at position due to the fact that it can be\nnull if the position is out of array bounds (this usually happens when all panels are hidden and we request an orientation change).\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43236", "files": ["mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/home/TabMenuStripLayout.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e4a1c144d595462f87eaa3923e28c6aab66a195b", "parents": ["cb92c46d1d5b479df80ca0565defa012ba6ac8ac"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003capehrson@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1573524 - In MediaRecorder::MediaStreamReady, get the graph rate from a track that's guaranteed live. r=padenot\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D42525", "files": ["dom/media/MediaRecorder.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "56e6a944c320a381b5ebfd66d7df3db5aaa6f40e", "parents": ["e4a1c144d595462f87eaa3923e28c6aab66a195b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "David Walsh \u003cdwalsh@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1575573 - Show addon icon in breakpoints pane r=jlast\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43070", "files": ["devtools/client/debugger/src/components/PrimaryPanes/SourcesTreeItem.js", "devtools/client/debugger/src/components/PrimaryPanes/tests/__snapshots__/SourcesTreeItem.spec.js.snap", "devtools/client/debugger/src/utils/source.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5c1b813d7ef5225e6cae63f8b7c9a9bde42e9ccd", "parents": ["56e6a944c320a381b5ebfd66d7df3db5aaa6f40e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Geoff Brown \u003cgbrown@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1575667 - Add --no-install option for android mach reftest and gtest; r=bc\n\nStraight-forward addition of the --no-install option for reftest, just like\nthe existing option for mochitest. For gtest, I alos noticed the mach command\nhelp needed some cleanup.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43299", "files": ["layout/tools/reftest/mach_commands.py", "layout/tools/reftest/reftestcommandline.py", "python/mozbuild/mozbuild/mach_commands.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c2be41ddc0be54e96ee12ade39b29514b6c17e96", "parents": ["5c1b813d7ef5225e6cae63f8b7c9a9bde42e9ccd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Kartikaya Gupta \u003ckgupta@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1564851 - Disable gfx.webrender.all.qualified by default.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43456", "files": ["gfx/thebes/gfxPlatform.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "025d1028313e06933dba9394650dc0f32c68e5e1", "parents": ["c2be41ddc0be54e96ee12ade39b29514b6c17e96"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nicolas Chevobbe \u003cnchevobbe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576563 - Evaluate selected text if a selection exists in console input. r=Honza.\n\nThis is something Scratchpad allowed and that people\ntold me they were relying on. With Scratchpad being\ndeprecated, it makes sense to implement it in the\nWebConsole as it's quite easy to do so.\nA test is added to ensure this works as expected.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43394", "files": ["devtools/client/webconsole/components/Input/JSTerm.js", "devtools/client/webconsole/test/browser/browser.ini", "devtools/client/webconsole/test/browser/browser_jsterm_editor_execute_selection.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0690321bae187ea4f67eb59acef2484c3ccf8b46", "parents": ["025d1028313e06933dba9394650dc0f32c68e5e1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nika Layzell \u003cnika@thelayzells.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1570369 - Part 12: Use IPDL refcoun