u \u003cxiaochengh@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574357 [wpt PR 18476] - Add parser and evaluation WPT for \u003cangle\u003e values involving min/max(), a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nAdd parser and evaluation WPT for \u003cangle\u003e values involving min/max()\n\nBug: 978682\nChange-Id: Ibee742e22ef09cf4762f519e5afc35b1a31acf7f\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/1757433\nCommit-Queue: Xiaocheng Hu \u003cxiaochengh@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Emil A Eklund \u003ceae@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#687788}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 76fa34dbf0f8b55df56d9c38d6ff7b2f5e37c318\nwpt-pr: 18476\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-values/minmax-angle-computed.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-values/minmax-angle-invalid.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "455eef93b909d7322a78f7966c915f26bdfdf942", "parents": ["131eefb43d0e78716ecaa43507ce2a280fd39ebf"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574357 [wpt PR 18476] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 18476\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-values/minmax-angle-computed.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2e16cf363b58330af214fe270b2a1c7cdd8f706a", "parents": ["455eef93b909d7322a78f7966c915f26bdfdf942"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Stephen McGruer \u003csmcgruer@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574615 [wpt PR 18508] - Fix interpolation-testcommon.js on Firefox, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nFix interpolation-testcommon.js on Firefox\n\nThe new test generation logic had some problems:\n\n  i. It produced different sets of tests on different browsers depending\n  on the support status. This caused difficulties comparing test results\n  across browsers.\n\n  ii. It produced duplicate subtest names when a 'from', 'to', or\n  'underlying' was not supported. Duplicate subtests are a fatal error\n  in WPT.\n\nThis CL fixes these problems by always generating the tests, and\nasserting support in them.\n\nIt also removes the composition code, which was unused.\n\nBug: 900581\nChange-Id: Id5617881bbf3b5f0a0b8eade5b630aa8fd65af8a\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/1758486\nCommit-Queue: Stephen McGruer \u003csmcgruer@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Robert Ma \u003crobertma@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#687797}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 6a439fd0334d0c7f57eb4cb58f29dbec1d026926\nwpt-pr: 18508\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/css/support/interpolation-testcommon.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cb469259185a77c44695a994be5a7c97f002aa64", "parents": ["2e16cf363b58330af214fe270b2a1c7cdd8f706a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574615 [wpt PR 18508] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 18508\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-sizing/animation/width-interpolation.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-transforms/animation/rotate-interpolation.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-transforms/animation/scale-interpolation.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-transforms/animation/translate-interpolation.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/motion/animation/offset-path-interpolation-005.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/motion/animation/offset-position-interpolation.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/feature-policy/experimental-features/layout-animations-disabled-tentative.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "70f199060a2b9f35754b1875ac31a123b1d14daa", "parents": ["cb469259185a77c44695a994be5a7c97f002aa64"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ian Kilpatrick \u003cikilpatrick@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": 