e-006.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-writing-modes/available-size-007.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-writing-modes/available-size-008.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-writing-modes/available-size-015.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-writing-modes/available-size-019.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "63db9fd42f978874648a29bf3587e4d3a0dc1b04", "parents": ["ca40c8c99cc24c6de561df40a9d5c24be7554088"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Florian Rivoal \u003cgit@florian.rivoal.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574772 [wpt PR 18527] - [css-writing-mode] Fix reftests, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\n[css-writing-mode] Fix reftests (#18527)\n\nThe reftests were correct with regards to size calculations,\nbut different writing modes align the viewport's scrollbar differently,\nand unless we compensate for that, thigns won't line up and ref-tests\nwill fail.\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 5f31d2e63a382fcd3d703123b1c76c4e25544fec\nwpt-pr: 18527\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-writing-modes/sizing-orthog-htb-in-vlr-004-ref.xht", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-writing-modes/sizing-orthog-htb-in-vlr-004.xht", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-writing-modes/sizing-orthog-htb-in-vrl-001-ref.xht"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d022e02c5d9b052d0141897d4620a382eb3f0fdb", "parents": ["63db9fd42f978874648a29bf3587e4d3a0dc1b04"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574772 [wpt PR 18527] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 18527\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-writing-modes/sizing-orthog-htb-in-vrl-001.xht.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-writing-modes/sizing-orthog-htb-in-vrl-004.xht.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a5abdd5cab87800635e614af1ff7c2fcb578f753", "parents": ["d022e02c5d9b052d0141897d4620a382eb3f0fdb"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Cathie Chen \u003ccathiechen@igalia.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574778 [wpt PR 18528] - Fixed nested list item crash when list-style-type:none, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nFixed nested list item crash when list-style-type:none\n\nIn quirks mode, if it's nested li, markers will occupy a whole line.\nIf list-style-type:none, it reasonable that no child in marker.\nSo remove the DCHECK and make marker_inline_size zero.\n\nBug: 985298\nChange-Id: I54281b70064a7a568ae8a3190c0244c1140462c6\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/1749266\nCommit-Queue: Koji Ishii \u003ckojii@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Koji Ishii \u003ckojii@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#687971}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: a7b9b0c0721a7ee59c58358fa0961ae7e38725fd\nwpt-pr: 18528\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-lists/nested-list-with-list-style-type-none.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e30261bb3546b21858ea7819477e31952702831b", "parents": ["a5abdd5cab87800635e614af1ff7c2fcb578f753"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Eric Willigers \u003cewilligers@users.noreply.github.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1572929 [wpt PR 18371] - [css-inline] Parsing line-height, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\n[css-inline] Parsing line-height (#18371)\n\nline-height is 'normal' or a number or a length-percentage.\n\nThe computed value for line-height is normal or a length.\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 11b9a030314227fa8e98ea76af85367357e86321\nwpt-pr: 18371\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-inline/parsing/line-height-computed.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-inline/parsing/line-height-invalid.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-inline/parsing/line-height-valid.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "18a1da56aa37da2d0d97dd5f6606a7e80132f4e6", "parents": ["e30261bb3546b2