601291a7946f2", "parents": ["d1fa7abcc2ec4dff6c644c4e71281bfb537f72f6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ali Juma \u003cajuma@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1573169 [wpt PR 18388] - Use get-host-info.sub.js in no-cross-origin-autofocus.sub.html, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nUse get-host-info.sub.js in no-cross-origin-autofocus.sub.html (#18388)\n\n* Use get-host-info.sub.js in no-cross-origin-autofocus.sub.html\n\nWebKit test infrastructure doesn't support domains like www1.localhost.\nThis change uses get_host_info().HTTP_REMOTE_ORIGIN to choose an\nappropriate cross-origin domain that works with both WPT infrastructure\nas well as with WebKit's test infrastructure.\n\nThis also removes 'sub' from this file name as it's no longer needed.\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: ee90e096375788bae5f83b4e7973632c9e3d48ef\nwpt-pr: 18388\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/html/semantics/forms/autofocus/no-cross-origin-autofocus.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/html/semantics/forms/autofocus/no-cross-origin-autofocus.sub.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8e4bb300a095fa624154b1ffb87bceed830b4938", "parents": ["3d9b8facd04f5ba2d3ae6fd78fa601291a7946f2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1573169 [wpt PR 18388] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 18388\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/html/semantics/forms/autofocus/no-cross-origin-autofocus.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/html/semantics/forms/autofocus/no-cross-origin-autofocus.sub.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "097e8b94b8445a3c119f9afdc61339ca41f524e0", "parents": ["8e4bb300a095fa624154b1ffb87bceed830b4938"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Anne van Kesteren \u003cannevk@annevk.nl\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574488 [wpt PR 18499] - HTML: \u003cimg\u003e's historical progress events, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nHTML: \u003cimg\u003e's historical progress events\n\nFor https://github.com/whatwg/html/pull/4842.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Philip J\u00e4genstedt \u003cphilip@foolip.org\u003e\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 76987cb3bb890c8691773ee7773cd150559ce594\nwpt-pr: 18499\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/html/semantics/embedded-content/the-img-element/historical-progress-event.window.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8bab9a7565f280ee038dda3708354cfddcbf1016", "parents": ["097e8b94b8445a3c119f9afdc61339ca41f524e0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574488 [wpt PR 18499] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 18499\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/html/semantics/embedded-content/the-img-element/historical-progress-event.window.js.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "47bd76faee77b06779e1d30d1404f186a43aa29d", "parents": ["8bab9a7565f280ee038dda3708354cfddcbf1016"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Dominik R\u00f6ttsches \u003cdrott@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574923 [wpt PR 18545] - Replace emoji with mathematical symbol in CSS selector ref test, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nReplace emoji with mathematical symbol in CSS selector ref test\n\nReplace the snowman emoji (U+2603) with the sum sign (U+2211) in order\nto avoid situations in which a color fallback font is chosen for the\nemoji, which cannot be colored white and the reftest thus failing, since\nthe test case shows and emoji, while the reference content does not\ncontain any characters.\n\nBug: 976737\nChange-Id: I342d81870418e56575700d3c0941a16544121a57\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/1760304\nAuto-Submit: Dominik R\u00f6ttsches \u003cdrott@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Rune Lillesveen \u003cfuthark@chromium.org\u003e\nCommit-Queue: Rune Lillesveen \u003cfuthark@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#688076}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: e697a7a9cbae673f3df19b603fe6c98e45057e7d\nwpt-pr: 18545\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/css/selectors/selectors-empty-001.xml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cb2b8c48dc55c2739028f0bd26a97b179748b18e", "parents": ["47bd76faee77b06779e1d30d1404f186a43aa29d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nicol\u00e1s Pe\u00f1a Moreno \u003cnpm@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574337 [wpt PR 18472] - [LargestContentfulPaint] Add larger content tests, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\n[LargestContentfulPaint] Add larger content tests\n\nThis CL adds tests where there is a bunch of content and LCP must observe the\nlargest (one for when image is largest, one for text).\n\nBug: 994414\nChange-Id: I9330f238e1f8a2a8227dce7a04fd741d2dc666d7\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/1757165\nReviewed-by: Steve Kobes \u003cskobes@chromium.org\u003e\nCommit-Queue: Nicol\u00e1s Pe\u00f1a Moreno \u003cnpm@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#688087}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 93e7ae091f09497c548ce60ca5026ef07c03b3bc\nwpt-pr: 18472\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/largest-contentful-paint/larger-image.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/largest-contentful-paint/larger-text.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "33a591a4b9a1440ffa70d0a3289428a0cf99ad26", "parents": ["cb2b8c48dc55c2739028f0bd26a97b179748b18e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574337 [wpt PR 18472] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 18472\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/largest-contentful-paint/larger-image.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/largest-contentful-paint/larger-text.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "361984cceb6672b15cfdcb8b9db3e4b84cb4a397", "