65c69fc942fcaeeae7ade05f605826c3\nwpt-pr: 18657\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/interfaces/pointerevents.idl"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5f72c43599b2dd500bc6c8e5650aeb2c3b5da082", "parents": ["58e816e855a39d41102f1852286655d0fb38d1b1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "autofoolip \u003cauto@foolip.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576436 [wpt PR 18658] - Update interfaces/webrtc-stats.idl, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nUpdate interfaces/webrtc-stats.idl (#18658)\n\nSource: https://github.com/tidoust/reffy-reports/blob/39e9fa7/whatwg/idl/webrtc-stats.idl\nBuild: https://travis-ci.org/tidoust/reffy-reports/builds/575681768\n--\n\nwpt-commits: e2fad5a488d3a489f962f2691af648edaa1a96ee\nwpt-pr: 18658\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/interfaces/webrtc-stats.idl"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b1fd9a1c85920b639839c74f511c99dd7d944988", "parents": ["5f72c43599b2dd500bc6c8e5650aeb2c3b5da082"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Eric Willigers \u003cewilligers@users.noreply.github.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576349 [wpt PR 18654] - [css-transforms] translate percent, reference box, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\n[css-transforms] translate percent, reference box (#18654)\n\nPercentages are relative to the width of the reference box (for the\nfirst value) or the height (for the second value).\nhttps://drafts.csswg.org/css-transforms-2/#propdef-translate\n\nTests are adapted from\ncss/css-transforms/transform-box/fill-box.html\ncss/css-transforms/transform-box/view-box.html\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 6933aa6626e5dbbe66a5c2b1835b511a6438a632\nwpt-pr: 18654\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-transforms/individual-transform/translate-fill-box.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-transforms/individual-transform/translate-view-box.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "df7557daf3d9ab43398c0f5654f0689539d15c94", "parents": ["b1fd9a1c85920b639839c74f511c99dd7d944988"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Adam Rice \u003cricea@chromium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574112 [wpt PR 18335] - Implement WebSocketStream, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nImplement WebSocketStream\n\nWebSocketStream is a new API for the WebSocket protocol that uses\nstreams to support backpressure.\n\nSee the explainer for more justification:\nhttps://github.com/ricea/websocketstream-explainer/blob/master/README.md\n\nThis CL implements WebSocketStream behind the\nexperimental-web-platform-features flag.\n\nSee the design doc at https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XuxEshh5VYBYm1qRVKordTamCOsR-uGQBCYFcHXP4L0/edit#heading=h.7nki9mck5t64\n\nBug: 983030\nChange-Id: I3002fd52ab151acb579e96a24985988e3fd35053\nReviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/1735156\nReviewed-by: Kinuko Yasuda \u003ckinuko@chromium.org\u003e\nReviewed-by: Yutaka Hirano \u003cyhirano@chromium.org\u003e\nCommit-Queue: Adam Rice \u003cricea@chromium.org\u003e\nCr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/master@{#690263}\n\n--\n\nwpt-commits: 23f463a0cc666d24bcb6b50ce2ab8b5deec77881\nwpt-pr: 18335\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/websockets/handlers/delayed-passive-close_wsh.py", "testing/web-platform/tests/websockets/stream-tentative/README.md", "testing/web-platform/tests/websockets/stream-tentative/close.any.js", "testing/web-platform/tests/websockets/stream-tentative/constructor.any.js", "testing/web-platform/tests/websockets/stream-tentative/resources/url-constants.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d9336d1a786623f2f8edbfbc22202b50cf2bb88f", "parents": ["df7557daf3d9ab43398c0f5654f0689539d15c94"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574112 [wpt PR 18335] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 18335\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/websockets/stream-tentative/clo