 a=release CLOSED TREE\n\nUpdate verify noticed the new comments in channel-prefs.js from bug 1576546, and thought they were significant. This change suppresses that by ignoring all lines starting with '//'. Since we can't match on the significant new line but not on the existing one we swallow a rat and comment the new whitespace.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44096", "files": ["browser/app/profile/channel-prefs.js", "tools/update-verify/release/compare-directories.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "04d54c74a7444cb8a3e90663b0e43b6593cf9c39", "parents": ["fc4326204da468558cfd3ad27bf420a0012b5c70"], "tags": ["DEVEDITION_70_0b2_BUILD2", "DEVEDITION_70_0b2_RELEASE"]}], "date": 1567137855, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "nthomas@mozilla.com"}, "11861": {"changesets": [{"author": "Nick Thomas \u003cnthomas@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577664 - mar-tools toolchain should depend on milestone.txt, r=Callek, a=release CLOSED TREE\n\nThe mar utility stores MOZ_APP_VERSION as the default Product Version for mar creation. So mar should be rebuilt whenever the milestone changes.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44089", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/toolchain/misc.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9017326fca65a042a30b4844bb458057f1300d75", "parents": ["04d54c74a7444cb8a3e90663b0e43b6593cf9c39"], "tags": []}], "date": 1567138527, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "nthomas@mozilla.com"}, "11862": {"changesets": [{"author": "Nick Thomas \u003cnthomas@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset 9017326fca65, a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/toolchain/misc.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cca944f1823e2703253b417e3130a397fc276a27", "parents": ["9017326fca65a042a30b4844bb458057f1300d75"], "tags": []}], "date": 1567138787, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "nthomas@