", "desc": "Bug 1522572 - Move local tab specifics out of TargetMixin. r=jdescottes,yulia\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D41854", "files": ["devtools/client/framework/target.js", "devtools/shared/fronts/root.js", "devtools/shared/fronts/targets/local-tab.js", "devtools/shared/fronts/targets/moz.build", "devtools/shared/fronts/targets/target-mixin.js", "devtools/shared/specs/root.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f975d273eabc226589fddf0f086c07fed3352f9f", "parents": ["2ed7ceca1578e6f2846537254fc29df107815f62"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nihanth Subramanya \u003cnhnt11@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574313 - Hide cookie subview category header if there's only one. r=johannh\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43336", "files": ["browser/base/content/browser-siteProtections.js", "browser/base/content/test/trackingUI/browser_trackingUI_cookies_subview.js", "browser/themes/shared/controlcenter/panel.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a34cb441dac0b4d07932a4b9d4074acbace29f87", "parents": ["f975d273eabc226589fddf0f086c07fed3352f9f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nihanth Subramanya \u003cnhnt11@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577419 - [Protections Panel] --height-offset should be 0px, not 0. r=johannh\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43928", "files": ["browser/themes/shared/controlcenter/panel.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8432696f30ea6dda39cb3af270ec81f3ef8da1b7", "parents": ["a34cb441dac0b4d07932a4b9d4074acbace29f87"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Frederic Wang \u003cfred.wang@free.fr\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1575870. Remove support for XLink on MathML elements. r=emilio\n\nSee https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/mozilla.dev.platform/70NFnet82cU\n\nThis commit introduces a new mathml.xlink.disabled option to disable support\nfor XLink attributes on MathML elements together with a use counter and\ndeprecation warning when support is enabled. For now, support is only disabled\nin Nighly.\n\nIn the past, we relied on custom MathML deprecation warnings but those are\nremoved here. Corresponding tests for these legacy warning messages are\nalso removed from test_bug553917.html.\n\nlink-1.xhtml is run with XLink support enabled (since it check xlink:href)\nwhile browser_contentAltClick.js is updated to check whether XLink has any\neffect on MathML, depending on whether the option is enabled.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43332", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/general/browser_contentAltClick.js", "dom/base/nsDeprecatedOperationList.h", "dom/locales/en-US/chrome/dom/dom.properties", "dom/locales/en-US/chrome/mathml/mathml.properties", "dom/mathml/nsMathMLElement.cpp", "layout/mathml/tests/test_bug553917.html", "layout/reftests/mathml/reftest.list", "modules/libpref/init/StaticPrefList.yaml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f20ce5c7a25c435989764808918e08e62ebada4e", "parents": ["8432696f30ea6dda39cb3af270ec81f3ef8da1b7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Razvan Maries \u003crmaries@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Merge mozilla-central to autoland. a=merge on a CLOSED TREE", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/webaudio/the-audio-api/the-mediastreamaudiosourcenode-interface/mediastreamaudiosourcenode-routing.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null, null], "node": "58e1a1d91db4b4adf058ede7d193dd825842c9f4", "parents": ["f20ce5c7a25c435989764808918e08e62ebada4e", "23824765c6aa026ccc3e3aea1c851c07ab8937ee"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Henri Sivonen \u003chsivonen@hsivonen.fi\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576895 - Update encoding_c to 0.9.1. r=m_kato\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43601", "files": ["Cargo.lock", "third_party/rust/encoding_c/.cargo-checksum.json", "third_party/rust/enco