d get an\nadditional aGraph argument. NotifyEnabledStateChanged is getting it too, for\ncompletion.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43667", "files": ["dom/media/MediaStreamGraph.cpp", "dom/media/MediaStreamListener.h", "dom/media/MediaStreamTrack.cpp", "dom/media/VideoOutput.h", "dom/media/encoder/MediaEncoder.cpp", "dom/media/imagecapture/CaptureTask.cpp", "dom/media/mediasink/DecodedStream.cpp", "dom/media/webspeech/recognition/SpeechTrackListener.cpp", "dom/media/webspeech/recognition/SpeechTrackListener.h", "media/webrtc/signaling/src/mediapipeline/MediaPipeline.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c9807cc4506756639c2d48803fa5fc302871bab6", "parents": ["85ef72ebde439c5de258af43faa9bd83a6e23b26"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003capehrson@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1573102 - Remove MediaStreamGraphImpl strong-refs from MediaEngineWebRTCAudio. r=karlt\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43668", "files": ["dom/media/webrtc/MediaEngineWebRTCAudio.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "08faaf9d4ef714eea2daea43c137cd02609830e5", "parents": ["c9807cc4506756639c2d48803fa5fc302871bab6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Sylvestre Ledru \u003csledru@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577236 - clang-10: Fix -Wimplicit-int-float-conversion warnings in /js/ r=jandem\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43783", "files": ["js/src/gc/Nursery.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fcc8383a1c4f04e0309463c778d6aeaa9aa7acdf", "parents": ["08faaf9d4ef714eea2daea43c137cd02609830e5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Honza Bambas \u003chonzab.moz@firemni.cz\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1559088 - Fix test_redirect-caching_failure.js to again do what it has to, r=kershaw\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43796", "files": ["netwerk/test/unit/test_redirect-caching_failure.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a4768bd82d57d0560d9f55750d0dc61822d4138d", "parents": ["fcc8383a1c4f04e0309463c778d6aeaa9aa7acdf"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Eric Rahm \u003cerahm@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1547108 - Remove warnings where we expect failures in nsJARChannel. r=mayhemer\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43828", "files": ["modules/libjar/nsJARChannel.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "070942b0a6d2612d6bc8eb637e8e12401db50e58", "parents": ["a4768bd82d57d0560d9f55750d0dc61822d4138d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Chris Manchester \u003ccmanchester@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577351 - Require a recent version of sccache when it is in use. r=nalexander\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43861", "files": ["build/moz.configure/toolchain.configure"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "daa065a75302e1d5aebbc5270cc50d6243aa7d3a", "parents": ["070942b0a6d2612d6bc8eb637e8e12401db50e58"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bogdan Tara \u003cbtara@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset a4768bd82d57 (bug 1559088) for test_redirect-caching_failure_wrap.js failures CLOSED TREE", "files": ["netwerk/test/unit/test_redirect-caching_failure.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "93ca7904bb6869892abf2bab9922e4507892972e", "parents": ["daa065a75302e1d5aebbc5270cc50d6243aa7d3a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jim Blandy \u003cjimb@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577355: Delete js::Zone::debuggers, which is unused. r=jonco\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43862", "files": ["js/src/debugger/Debugger.cpp", "js/src/gc/Zone.cpp", "js/src/gc/Zone.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f3ea3487dbe1ca923600029b2133965e77b6d7fe", "parents": ["93ca7904bb6869892abf2bab9922e4507892972e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Boris Zbarsky \u003cbzbarsky@mit.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577560.  Change the key setup for the document's id and name table to not copy string keys on lookup.  r=mccr8.\n\nIn the old setup, a lookup with an nsAString key would implicitly construct an\nAtomOrString, which would assign the key to an nsString.  This would lead to\ncopies and heap-allocations if the key was an autostring, which it typically is\nwhen coming from bindings.\n\nThis fix improves the performance of the new window-named-property-get.html pref\nreftest by about 20-30%, and improves the new getElementById-1.html test by 2-3x.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44015", "files": ["dom/base/Document.cpp", "dom/base/IdentifierMapEntry.h", "testing/talos/talos/tests/perf-reftest-singletons/getElementById-1.html", "testing/talos/talos/tests/perf-reftest-singletons/perf_reftest_singletons.manifest", "testing/talos/talos/tests/perf-reftest-singletons/window-named-property-get.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "03cc4203321f4f63d08bf290d697e433b72be972", "parents": ["f3ea3487dbe1ca923600029b2133965e77b6d7fe"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erica Wright \u003cewright@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576562 - Convert icons from background-image so they are displayed in high contrast mode. r=johannh\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43669", "files": ["browser/components/protections/content/protections.css", "browser/components/protections/content/protections.html", "browser/components/protections/content/protections.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1268324809b4f36078337193ab7becc3e67fffb3", "parents": ["03cc4203321f4f63d08bf290d697e433b72be972"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Erica Wright \u003cewright@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577462 - Update about:preferences privacy top level description. r=flod,fl