ckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/geckoview/WebPushController.java", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/geckoview/WebPushDelegate.java", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/geckoview/WebPushSubscription.java", "mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/geckoview/doc-files/CHANGELOG.md", "mobile/android/geckoview_example/src/main/java/org/mozilla/geckoview_example/GeckoViewActivity.java", "mobile/android/installer/package-manifest.in", "mobile/android/modules/geckoview/GeckoViewPushController.jsm", "mobile/android/modules/geckoview/moz.build", "testing/web-platform/meta/push-api/idlharness.https.any.js.ini", "widget/android/Base64UtilsSupport.h", "widget/android/nsAppShell.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6390dc77aaf0a3cb47f40227e8e0da858facdcff", "parents": ["776a6309e975921cd939ffcf03dc037be499f2eb"], "tags": []}, {"author": "David Walsh \u003cdwalsh@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577081 - Make blackbox work from frame context menu r=jlast\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43973", "files": ["devtools/client/debugger/src/components/SecondaryPanes/Frames/Frame.js", "devtools/client/debugger/src/components/SecondaryPanes/Frames/FrameMenu.js", "devtools/client/debugger/src/components/SecondaryPanes/Frames/Group.js", "devtools/client/debugger/src/components/SecondaryPanes/Frames/tests/Frame.spec.js", "devtools/client/debugger/src/components/SecondaryPanes/Frames/tests/FrameMenu.spec.js", "devtools/client/debugger/src/components/SecondaryPanes/Frames/tests/Group.spec.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "61e550aaa29d07a4e5a57dd75be5eaa7e8c1194c", "parents": ["6390dc77aaf0a3cb47f40227e8e0da858facdcff"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrew Halberstadt \u003cahalberstadt@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577588 - [taskgraph] Add an index route for shadow scheduler tasks, r=jmaher\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44027", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/source-test/shadow-scheduler.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "85d8c19fcc3c712b4c3515568a08688d968f7d7f", "parents": ["61e550aaa29d07a4e5a57dd75be5eaa7e8c1194c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577258 - Explicitly flush layout in an a11y test. r=eeejay\n\nWe have an optimization to avoid an expensive reflow from SetFullZoom, see\nmSuppressResizeReflow[1].\n\nThat was done because we used to do a full synchronous reflow right after. We no\nlonger do that, but due to that member we also don't invalidate!\n\nMy second patch in this bug changes the behavior of that flag so that we don't\nsynchronously reflow, but we do invalidate. So in turn this test before the\nchange wasn't really testing the zoomed code-path since it was using the clean\nlayout from before the zoom operation.\n\na11y getBounds and co. don't flush layout (they probably should), but since with\nmy patch we dirty the frame tree, and dirty frames return bogus offsets, the\ntest starts failing.\n\nFlush layout explicitly to ensure we're testing the zoomed code path.\n\n[1]: https://searchfox.org/mozilla-central/rev/325c1a707819602feff736f129cb36055ba6d94f/layout/base/nsPresContext.cpp#952\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43952", "files": ["accessible/tests/mochitest/hittest/test_zoom_text.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "49ff97acd5ce9f094430bf4538e7f32792201182", "parents": ["85d8c19fcc3c712b4c3515568a08688d968f7d7f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Sylvestre Ledru \u003csledru@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577629 - Rename job \"cpp\" to \"cppunit\" r=ahal\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44048", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/test/compiled.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5202fd3daa100d65960e7f28e70da17672460413", "parents": ["49ff97acd5ce9f094430bf4538e7f32792201182"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Eric Willigers \u003cewilligers@users.noreply.github.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1571197 [wpt PR 18271] - [css-grid] Parsing grid-template-rows/columns, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\n[css-grid] Parsing grid-template-rows/columns (#18271)\n\nTest parsing of valid and invalid values for\ngrid-template-rows and grid-template-columns\nValue:\tnone | \u003ctrack-list\u003e | \u003cauto-track-list\u003e\nhttps://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/#track-sizing\n--\n\nwpt-commits: eec73456c88a03b12d566b2a2f4dcfd1f4138b55\nwpt-pr: 18271\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-grid/parsing/grid-template-columns-invalid.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-grid/parsing/grid-template-columns-valid.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-grid/parsing/grid-template-rows-invalid.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-grid/parsing/grid-template-rows-valid.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8a48ca1e3378031c8f33fdf60e7158a961939ab8", "parents": ["23824765c6aa026ccc3e3aea1c851c07ab8937ee"], "tags": []}, {"author": "moz-wptsync-bot \u003cwptsync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1571197 [wpt PR 18271] - Update wpt metadata, a=testonly\n\nwpt-pr: 18271\nwpt-type: metadata\n", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-grid/parsing/grid-template-columns-valid.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-grid/parsing/grid-template-rows-valid.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ab0df4902c62a9c9b5a6a6038fd0c3a521b637d9", "parents": ["8a48ca1e3378031c8f33fdf60e7158a961939ab8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Wang \u003cfwang@igalia.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576571 [wpt PR 18666] - MathML margin/border/padding: verify that they are taken into account\u2026, a=testonly\n\nAutomatic update from web-platform-tests\nMathML margin/border/paddi