es empty for new rule inspector. r=pbro\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43721", "files": ["devtools/client/inspector/rules/new-rules.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "703a2947c350dc4e9d7426893894c725c7147eed", "parents": ["822638e9789acfdf47a0c0103a485a9bc4b0fcf1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daisuke Akatsuka \u003cdaisuke@birchill.co.jp\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1543782: Add tests in case of empty. r=pbro\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43722", "files": ["devtools/client/inspector/rules/test/browser.ini", "devtools/client/inspector/rules/test/browser_rules_completion-on-empty.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2081fd72fd28579d4f75e5faa43744fa6fc83808", "parents": ["703a2947c350dc4e9d7426893894c725c7147eed"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daisuke Akatsuka \u003cdaisuke@birchill.co.jp\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1543782: Add test for the shortcut key which shows the suggest completion popup. r=pbro\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43723", "files": ["devtools/client/inspector/rules/test/browser.ini", "devtools/client/inspector/rules/test/browser_rules_completion-shortcut.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d7b6b036d777c0d3290f5d923a987f2cefebff73", "parents": ["2081fd72fd28579d4f75e5faa43744fa6fc83808"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nick Thomas \u003cnthomas@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577664 - mar-tools toolchain should depend on milestone.txt, r=Callek\n\nThe mar utility stores MOZ_APP_VERSION as the default Product Version for mar creation. So mar should be rebuilt whenever the milestone changes.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44089", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/toolchain/misc.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "464a2ec59a588b659465e61c2e65e39046924e53", "parents": ["d7b6b036d777c0d3290f5d923a987f2cefebff73"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Noemi Erli \u003cnerli@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset 464a2ec59a58 (bug 1577664) for causing gecko decision task failure", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/toolchain/misc.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d9a8ec2b7cd8d8d6ee4476db5e78ab872ccd7bac", "parents": ["464a2ec59a588b659465e61c2e65e39046924e53"], "tags": []}, {"author": "James Teh \u003cjteh@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574286: When adding a remote child document, if the parent proxy doesn't exist yet, defer adding until it does. r=eeejay\n\nFor OOP iframes, sometimes, AddChildDoc gets called before the embedder sends us the OuterDocAccessible.\nPreviously, we crashed when this occurred.\nNow, we add the child when the OuterDocAccessible proxy gets created later.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D42798", "files": ["accessible/ipc/DocAccessibleParent.cpp", "accessible/ipc/DocAccessibleParent.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "952b14eb6ea33af77240fb8eab0b2e6f5f6181bd", "parents": ["d9a8ec2b7cd8d8d6ee4476db5e78ab872ccd7bac"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nick Thomas \u003cnthomas@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577664 - pass product version to the complete mar generation script, r=Callek\n\nMOZ_FULL_PRODUCT_VERSION is only used here, while tools/update-packaging/make_full_update.sh expects MOZ_PRODUCT_VERSION.\n\nDepends on D44089\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44090", "files": ["python/mozbuild/mozbuild/repackaging/mar.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ca2208744242590c1350dd7c217d5db4cfbfc8cf", "parents": ["952b14eb6ea33af77240fb8eab0b2e6f5f6181bd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "James Teh \u003cjteh@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1575749: Implement toolbar navigation by typed character. r=Gijs\n\nWhen focused on a toolbar button, users can now type the first (or first few) characters of another button's name to jump directly to that button.\nThe search characters are cleared after 1 second or if a non-character key is pressed.\nThis is similar to the typed character navigation implemented for HTML select controls.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43187", "files": ["browser/base/content/browser-toolbarKeyNav.js", "browser/base/content/test/keyboard/browser_toolbarKeyNav.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9424c2a92af4b3838f0d8d352042018b890a9f65", "parents": ["ca2208744242590c1350dd7c217d5db4cfbfc8cf"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Cameron Kaiser \u003cspectre@floodgap.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576303 - Temporary compiler workaround for crashes on ppc64le. r=tcampbell\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43715", "files": ["js/src/gc/Barrier.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4559e60f4ddebbe462b4aa5569849a404b29cafa", "parents": ["9424c2a92af4b3838f0d8d352042018b890a9f65"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bogdan Tara \u003cbtara@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset 80bb50e715a3 (bug 1550122) for browser_loginItemErrors.js failures", "files": ["browser/components/BrowserGlue.jsm", "browser/components/aboutlogins/AboutLoginsChild.jsm", "browser/components/aboutlogins/AboutLoginsParent.jsm", "browser/components/aboutlogins/content/aboutLogins.html", "browser/components/aboutlogins/content/aboutLogins.js", "browser/components/aboutlogins/content/components/login-item.css", "browser/components/aboutlogins/content/components/login-item.js", "browser/components/aboutlogins/tests/browser/browser.ini", "browser/components/aboutlogins/tests/browser/browser_loginItemErrors.js", "browser/locales/en-US/browser/aboutLogins.ftl"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ce8d92d5a45b48b2d191503dcc73dc844bd6986a", "parents": ["4559e60f4ddebbe462b4aa5569849a404b29cafa"