ia-activedescendant when mousing over one-off search buttons. r=mak\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44162", "files": ["browser/components/search/content/search-one-offs.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d116943004375716e43e6863d8a4b375821c7eaa", "parents": ["39b55da47051eb9be3f4ad663ee1c4deb1c51245"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nicolas Silva \u003cnsilva@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1562869 - Check for NaNs in project_rect. r=aosmond\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44114", "files": ["gfx/wr/webrender/src/util.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9a59db93153408008285cac6cb17bf9d84b86aca", "parents": ["d116943004375716e43e6863d8a4b375821c7eaa"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nihanth Subramanya \u003cnhnt11@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576100 - Ensure correct document order of category items for keyboard nav. r=johannh\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43932", "files": ["browser/base/content/browser-siteProtections.js", "browser/base/content/test/siteProtections/browser_protections_UI.js", "browser/components/controlcenter/content/protectionsPanel.inc.xul", "browser/themes/shared/controlcenter/panel.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "274f8d9b14b6eb32368010c386a59c16fcc6ccc4", "parents": ["9a59db93153408008285cac6cb17bf9d84b86aca"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nihanth Subramanya \u003cnhnt11@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577622 - Open and close the Allowed - Why? tooltip on focus/blur. r=johannh\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44040", "files": ["browser/components/controlcenter/content/protectionsPanel.inc.xul"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "202b771061fb165810bdc2e9f0f220535f43e2e0", "parents": ["274f8d9b14b6eb32368010c386a59c16fcc6ccc4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Rob Wu \u003crob@ro