u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1564499 - land NSS NSS_3_46_RTM UPGRADE_NSS_RELEASE, r=kjacobs\n\n2019-08-30  J.C. Jones  \u003cjjones@mozilla.com\u003e\n\n\t* lib/nss/nss.h, lib/softoken/softkver.h, lib/util/nssutil.h:\n\tSet version numbers to 3.46 final\n\t[decbf7bd40fd] [NSS_3_46_RTM]\n\n2019-08-27  J.C. Jones  \u003cjjones@mozilla.com\u003e\n\n\t* .hgtags:\n\tAdded tag NSS_3_46_BETA2 for changeset 24b0fc700203\n\t[29cd579e74e4]\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44206", "files": ["security/nss/TAG-INFO", "security/nss/coreconf/coreconf.dep", "security/nss/lib/nss/nss.h", "security/nss/lib/softoken/softkver.h", "security/nss/lib/util/nssutil.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "86e573da81d122f34633000e966839054c5f72f6", "parents": ["782e541cd664f6b86b0644b2f311e5c391ef9d2a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Sebastian Hengst \u003carchaeopteryx@coole-files.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577727 - set meta data in which bugzilla product & component debugger bugs should be filed. r=jlast DONTBUILD\n\nGot (accidentally?) removed in bug 1500987.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44119", "files": ["devtools/client/debugger/moz.build"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a8ae9fef77a46f96c517bdb2620e9f4cff071afc", "parents": ["86e573da81d122f34633000e966839054c5f72f6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Henning \u003cjh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1548776 - URL-decode all file names in GeckoJarReader. r=snorp\n\nAssuming the URL string the JAR reader receives has been completely URL-encoded,\nwe need to decode not just the first nested jarUrl, as already happens through\ngetZipFile(), but all subsequent path components, too.\n\nAt least for jar:-URLs received from Gecko, the above assumption certainly seems\nto be true.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44033", "files": ["mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/gecko/util/GeckoJarReader.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cd343dac2978e474019c52761afc9e7b9adb76d7", "parents": ["a8ae9fef77a46f96c517bdb2620e9f4cff071afc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nathan Froyd \u003cfroydnj@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576751 - set LD_LIBRARY_PATH during Android builds; r=glandium\n\nWe need this for host binaries to work correctly in the case where the\nclang we're using is linking against a newer version of, say,\n`libstdc++` than is on the system.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43529", "files": ["mobile/android/config/mozconfigs/common"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "99451e6294fa57000bd442c9f3851be6d1d73a1e", "parents": ["cd343dac2978e474019c52761afc9e7b9adb76d7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Paul Bone \u003cpbone@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577194 - Skip the postMessage tests for fission r=mccr8\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44092", "files": ["dom/tests/mochitest/whatwg/mochitest.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "663df1e9e579f46a9d68156350ce89911f9dc520", "parents": ["99451e6294fa57000bd442c9f3851be6d1d73a1e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Honza Bambas \u003chonzab.moz@firemni.cz\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1559088 - Fix test_redirect-caching_failure.js to again do what it has to, r=kershaw\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43796", "files": ["netwerk/test/unit/test_redirect-caching_failure.js", "netwerk/test/unit_ipc/test_redirect-caching_failure_wrap.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9057d052aceef4771b6717a4631f30cd887e3159", "parents": ["663df1e9e579f46a9d68156350ce89911f9dc520"], "tags": []}, {"author": "tanhengyeow \u003cE0032242@u.nus.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1561873 - Support for keyboard navigation in WS frame list. r=Honza\