e MediaStreamGraphs individual ShutdownBlockers. r=karlt a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44380", "files": ["dom/media/MediaStreamGraph.cpp", "dom/media/MediaStreamGraphImpl.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "02bc71fde278c94227ad2f05503e72a96abb62b5", "parents": ["f7b7283f9bee41c02178abd2311bd7eb60b5e778"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ryan Hunt \u003crhunt@eqrion.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1578031 - Correct return type for `GetOffsetGuardLimit`. r=lth a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44311", "files": ["js/src/jit/arm/MacroAssembler-arm.cpp", "js/src/jit/arm64/MacroAssembler-arm64.cpp", "js/src/jit/mips-shared/MacroAssembler-mips-shared.cpp", "js/src/jit/mips32/MacroAssembler-mips32.cpp", "js/src/jit/mips64/MacroAssembler-mips64.cpp", "js/src/jit/x64/CodeGenerator-x64.cpp", "js/src/jit/x86/CodeGenerator-x86.cpp", "js/src/wasm/WasmTypes.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6cdaee1535a1b66ad6bd44c7f78ea77ccfdfa4ac", "parents": ["02bc71fde278c94227ad2f05503e72a96abb62b5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tim Nguyen \u003cntim.bugs@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1578324 - Cleanup some text-align properties in about:logins. r=jaws a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44509", "files": ["browser/components/aboutlogins/content/components/login-filter.css", "browser/components/aboutlogins/content/components/login-item.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "62a886e8b21ea1508f8bb41492d6e034c84afd2d", "parents": ["6cdaee1535a1b66ad6bd44c7f78ea77ccfdfa4ac"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1574718 - Cycle-collect inline-sheet cache. r=heycam a=lizzard\n\nThis is an oversight from the initial implementation of the cache.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.co