tantially reduces the max GC heap size while running these tests as well as vsize and RSS. Hopefully this will fix the problem with the tests failing while we work out a good solution for the underlying issue.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44378", "files": ["dom/base/nsJSEnvironment.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "df3bfb6c871b0023a7f7b75993e5f16e8cadacc8", "parents": ["36b891a1c27e083fca0c5eb22cf9146373c4d61c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Dzmitry Malyshau \u003cdmalyshau@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1579227 - Switch YUV images to be opaque in WR r=jrmuizel a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D45030", "files": ["gfx/wr/webrender/src/prim_store/image.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a23c865aef7f1e42922d14be7287a8c068064aea", "parents": ["df3bfb6c871b0023a7f7b75993e5f16e8cadacc8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Paul Adenot \u003cpaul@paul.cx\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1572878 - Compute the reverb on the main thread. r=karlt a=lizzard\n\nThis is necessary to keep the invariant that once the setter returns, the reverb\nis ready to process.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D43476", "files": ["dom/media/webaudio/ConvolverNode.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bebd155150c88baa2743810bde5d1f3615a08f5f", "parents": ["a23c865aef7f1e42922d14be7287a8c068064aea"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nika Layzell \u003cnika@thelayzells.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577711 - Part 1: Revert calling SetDocument earlier during clone from 1568055, r=smaug a=lizzard\n\nThis change was causing issues with images not displaying and iframes not\ndisplaying correctly after multiple print preview calls.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44585", "files": ["dom/base/Document.cpp", "dom/base/nsFrameLoader.cpp", "layout/printing/nsPrintObject.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "468cfd64d1034e460c41fef14f665edd392bdb4d", "parents": ["bebd155150c88baa2743810bde5d1f3615a08f5f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nika Layzell \u003cnika@thelayzells.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577711 - Part 2: Perform frame static clone after parent static clone, r=smaug a=lizzard\n\nThis is done by delaying the code within nsFrameLoader::CreateStaticClone until\nafter the document has been created. The nsFrameLoader is re-discovered using\nthe subframe BrowsingContext's mEmbedderElement.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44586", "files": ["dom/base/nsFrameLoader.cpp", "dom/base/nsFrameLoader.h", "layout/printing/nsPrintJob.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7ba2b66f0e32ff4e86ad140f2b25ae7c7eeeffb4", "parents": ["468cfd64d1034e460c41fef14f665edd392bdb4d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003capehrson@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577184 - Guard against a shutting down AudioContext in MediaElementAudioSourceNode. r=karlt a=lizzard\n\nDepends on D44486\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44487", "files": ["dom/media/webaudio/MediaElementAudioSourceNode.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5cb53f0ec73138c7143b8f5bbd6aacd9ff7ec653", "parents": ["7ba2b66f0e32ff4e86ad140f2b25ae7c7eeeffb4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Marco Zehe \u003cmzehe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1579126 - Make the Allowed section heading in the protections panel a heading for screen readers as well, r=nhnt11 a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44860", "files": ["browser/components/controlcenter/content/protectionsPanel.inc.xul"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "36a40d4ffc208e1d4116467e036e515733dbd9a2", "parents": ["5cb53f0ec73138c7143b8f5bbd6aacd9ff7ec653"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576524 - Have APZCTreeManager track a set of layers ids for which it should not send MatrixMessages. r=tnikkel,hsivonen a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44740", "files": ["gfx/layers/apz/public/APZUpdater.h", "gfx/layers/apz/src/APZCTreeManager.cpp", "gfx/layers/apz/src/APZCTreeManager.h", "gfx/layers/apz/src/APZUpdater.cpp", "gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorBridgeParent.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "70f42eeac8f3ac07e5fa9a25fe149f3af2d478a0", "parents": ["36a40d4ffc208e1d4116467e036e515733dbd9a2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1576524 - Clean up APZCTreeManager::mDetachedLayersIds in UpdateHitTestingTree. r=tnikkel a=lizzard\n\nThis ensures that mDetachedLayersIds doesn't grow indefinitely.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44741", "files": ["gfx/layers/apz/src/APZCTreeManager.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b3b3d3c3b47c73be4d326e04d9e88e3afd55299a", "parents": ["70f42eeac8f3ac07e5fa9a25fe149f3af2d478a0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tom Ritter \u003ctom@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1579495 - Remove Nightly guards on eval telemetry r=ckerschb a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com//D45065", "files": ["caps/nsScriptSecurityManager.cpp", "dom/security/CSPEvalChecker.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2a11b5cf25b3409a68e3317446e8c2d8cf92a7ec", "parents": ["b3b3d3c3b47c73be4d326e04d9e88e3afd55299a"], "tags": []}], "date": 1568236944, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "cbrindusan@mozilla.com"}, "11929": {"changesets": [{"author": "Andreas Pehrson \u003capehrson@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1577184 - Add crashtest. r=karlt a=lizzard\n\nDifferential