leans up the display to make it quicker to find\nwhat changed, especially with large numbers of tabs. The bit of\nnew information that I'm particularly interested in is what\nevent triggered a particular update - so now every time we call\npostActions, we include the name of the event.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D44710", "files": ["browser/base/content/docs/tabbrowser/async-tab-switcher.rst", "browser/modules/AsyncTabSwitcher.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6e1216ffc35ad6e45b0cf6cfe6775dd1d7adb1ef", "parents": ["6249300e94a498cb8c3fb9425bf89e76f6d1e055"], "tags": []}], "date": 1568299565, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ncsoregi@mozilla.com"}, "11941": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\ncy -\u003e 047f0fe84d2f\nhsb -\u003e 8fbc488ded7d\nit -\u003e 737dc0a0af35\nja -\u003e d08854d91cd6\nnb-NO -\u003e 591ad0388757\nnn-NO -\u003e 95b42c1cb5dc\npt-BR -\u003e 040308bdd48d\nzh-CN -\u003e 00517e6a4aa4\nzh-TW -\u003e 61442c7f19e4", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f63d5dbf83166abecb4d37e134fb06bd88e1e227", "parents": ["6e1216ffc35ad6e45b0cf6cfe6775dd1d7adb1ef"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\ncy -\u003e 047f0fe84d2f\nhsb -\u003e 8fbc488ded7d\nia -\u003e 4d4ce5cdb357\nit -\u003e 737dc0a0af35\nja -\u003e d08854d91cd6\nja-JP-mac -\u003e 8b741949e4ca\nnb-NO -\u003e 591ad0388757\nnn-NO -\u003e 95b42c1cb5dc\npt-BR -\u003e 040308bdd48d\nzh-CN -\u003e 00517e6a4aa4\nzh-TW -\u003e 61442c7f19e4", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c45820c3cb53ba51d48678e2a45eb9ee504b0852", 