rd\n\n* Updates the frequency cap for the extended triplets feature\n* Updates the experiment ID\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D47653", "files": ["browser/components/newtab/lib/ASRouter.jsm", "browser/components/newtab/lib/OnboardingMessageProvider.jsm", "browser/components/newtab/test/unit/asrouter/ASRouter.test.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6de5423ca135a7a99837c06f4ab1e854f98d2b1a", "parents": ["bfd2fa321e1200b0cb29c0e7ebda958a90e2c626"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nihanth Subramanya \u003cnhnt11@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1584633 - Add hover/active states to the TP switch background. r=johannh a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D47506", "files": ["browser/themes/shared/controlcenter/panel.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "17b4f7b2c9697d78f98a702572864bd96001d1e0", "parents": ["6de5423ca135a7a99837c06f4ab1e854f98d2b1a"], "tags": []}], "date": 1570043742, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "12091": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mike Hommey \u003cmh+mozilla@glandium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1580533 - Ensure MOZ_CONFIGURE_OPTIONS is unicode. r=chmanchester a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D47709", "files": ["toolkit/moz.configure"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ca06dcc43bb7e5b3be232a2a4050de9d5732da09", "parents": ["17b4f7b2c9697d78f98a702572864bd96001d1e0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Harry Twyford \u003chtwyford@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1582396 - Set width correctly on the searchbar autocomplete in the overflow menu. r=dao a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D46488", "files": ["browser/components/search/content/autocomplete-popup.js", "browser/components/search/content/searchbar.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "074e38c710b9f00cf41056d58e58e7c84630444f", "parents": ["ca06dcc43bb7e5b3be232a2a4050de9d5732da09"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Harry Twyford \u003chtwyford@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1584336 - Re-add the width attribute to the searchbar. r=dao a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D47624", "files": ["browser/components/search/content/searchbar.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c0a9eaf7c5a5f67fec2967f9a15ee57a03ecb118", "parents": ["074e38c710b9f00cf41056d58e58e7c84630444f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tim Huang \u003ctihuang@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1578093 - Change the margin end of the ideneity box to 2px from 4px in oder to make the lock icon looks more centered. r=johannh a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D47593", "files": ["browser/themes/shared/identity-block/identity-block.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "37355d143d67b0d9353cc94b7da33d411de6a3de", "parents": ["c0a9eaf7c5a5f67fec2967f9a15ee57a03ecb118"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tim Huang \u003ctihuang@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1578334 - Update the tooltip of the tracking protection icon when toggling the TP switch. r=nhnt11 a=lizzard\n\nIn order to show a correct tooltip after toggling the TP switch. We\nupdate the tooltip of the tracking protection icon when toggling the TP\nswitch right before the 500 ms waiting.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D47587", "files": ["browser/base/content/browser-siteProtections.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b3d633c3bb7510ee6cb12c939add794ce97abdd0", "parents": ["37355d143d67b0d9353cc94b7da33d411de6a3de"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1575138 - Do not schedule reconstruction for \u003cslot\u003e if there's no fallback. r=smaug a=lizzard\n\nJust realized that we probably want this too.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D46898", "files": ["dom/base/ShadowRoot.cpp", "layout/base/PresShell.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b63b75ad69b6a5a7d72811a9971f0f7555379905", "parents": ["b3d633c3bb7510ee6cb12c939add794ce97abdd0"], "tags": []}], "date": 1570045221, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "dvarga@mozilla.com"}, "12092": {"changesets": [{"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1575138 - Don't bother scheduling a reconstruct on \u003cslot\u003es that have no fallback. r=smaug a=lizzard\n\nSo basically what's going on is that we remove all children from the popup here:\n\n  https://searchfox.org/mozilla-central/rev/153feabebc2d13bb4c29ef8adf104ec1ebd246ae/browser/base/content/browser-places.js#687\n\nThis makes us schedule a reconstruct of the slot, in case it has fallback\ncontent:\n\n  https://searchfox.org/mozilla-central/rev/153feabebc2d13bb4c29ef8adf104ec1ebd246ae/dom/base/ShadowRoot.cpp#616\n\nThen we insert frames for the items. They get inserted right away, because we\ndon't support lazy frame construction for XUL:\n\n  https://searchfox.org/mozilla-central/rev/153feabebc2d13bb4c29ef8adf104ec1ebd246ae/layout/base/nsCSSFrameConstructor.cpp#6507\n\nIf this was normal HTML content, the insertion would've been lazy, and no\nreconstruct would've happened.\n\nThe right fix is to support lazy frame construction for XUL. Now that there's\nvery little XBL it should be possible. This fixes it but it's a kind-of stop-gap\nsolution.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D46825", "files": ["dom/base/ShadowRoot.cpp", "layout/base/PresShell.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "35832cb16061a8b2b3da5ba8e4859df9a13f8ffc", "parents": ["b63b75ad69b6a5a7d72811a9971f0f7555379905"], 